The paper discusses the interoperability and integration between the XML and Semantic Web worlds, which involves data modeling, semantics, and query languages. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), and software engineering (cs.SE).
